This module extends module ir_sequence_option and allow you to
provide optional sequences for hr.expense.sheet documents.

.. IMPORTANT::
   This is an alpha version, the data model and design can change at any time without warning.
   Only for development or testing purpose, do not use in production.
   `More details on development status <https://odoo-community.org/page/development-status>`_

===========

`feedback <https://github.com/OCA/hr-expense/issues/new?body=module:%20hr_expense_sequence_option%0Aversion:%2014.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**>`_.
